data.title: 3244 Petronius
data.meta_description: is an asteroid found in the main belt, a member of the Flora family of asteroids. It was discovered by Cornelis Johannes van Houten, Ingrid van Houten Groeneveld and Tom Gehrels in 1960. It is named after Petronius Arbiter, the ancient Roman…
